sig_info: When Sentry loses his Combo, he has a 26.5 to 100% chance to become Indestructible for 0.30 seconds per Reality Warp. Indestructible doesn’t trigger if Sentry is afflicted with a Debuff.
At the start of a fight, if Health is above 89.09 to 0%, Reality Warps persist with Sentry from the previous fight.
